Title: HW/SW Inventory: Inventory data from remote sites was not always up-to-date
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: liveproxy
Date: 1592312803
Edition: cee
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.0.0i1

The liveproxyd (which handles the HW/SW data synchronization) only reliably
synchronized the HW/SW inventory data from remote sites upon restart/reload.


Note: A liveproxyd reload is triggered whenever the user makes changes in the WATO site configuration.
